{"tid":445320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★正式玩完！Apple 腰斬 iPhone 8 訂單","createTime":"2017-10-23T09:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T16:50:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"946b779729db9dcbe07680e112886697d0d3ec83","tid":445320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"iPhone 8 上市已經快一個月了，但是由於用戶反映的各種 bug 和電池膨脹問題，導致 iPhone 8 口碑一落千丈。加上大部分買家對 iPhone X 的等待，導致 iPhone 8 銷量持續低迷。而 Apple 歷史首次提前降低 iPhone 新品訂單量。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Apple 供應鏈最新消息顯示，由於 iPhone 8 系列不如預期的銷量，所以在11月、12月當中，供應鏈會下調 iPhone 8 系列的訂單量，數量會下調一半之多。供應鏈也表示，在開售三個月內就被要求降低訂單量，對於 Apple 來說還是10年以來頭一次。不過對此消息，iPhone 8 的主力供貨商，和碩與緯創並沒有出面解釋。目前 Apple 放低了 iPhone 8 的期待<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2017/10/20/apple-cut-iphone-8-order/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2Fapple-cut-iphone-8-order%2F&d=mStNS%2BUU0P4YCm3kKkotsG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=03b1634b\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2017/10/20/apple-cut-iphone-8-order/</a>"},{"pid":"8c9eb038cb776a1aca647a5cbe250d3bc27e296d","tid":445320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842d3baf30e510fada5f36e498f0918cfa31042f","tid":445320,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d40ed53a0fc38eba85750f9c199b6899fb0c303","tid":445320,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23edfe7a4cab65538d3c00906912d8407a5a486e","tid":445320,"uid":55597,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T10:25:50.000Z","msg":"apple 可能特登做衰 8 等 x 賣得多"},{"pid":"3fb4db35694e6ca11d9510d79308f87bd8461568","tid":445320,"uid":130513,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7450e919d0adaa3b38dd47f18ed4610433c5cb1","tid":445320,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:15:03.000Z","msg":"老貓，全球期待iPhone X"},{"pid":"54a755d96bf302ded7a92a1dab6332fe6c5fc355","tid":445320,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:16:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓，全球期待iPhone X</blockquote><br />\n期待 閱文招股多d"},{"pid":"2428d5af0334d573d5db866e46bb43347a7ae533","tid":445320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>apple 可能特登做衰 8 等 x 賣得多</blockquote><br />\n華為 賣多左就真"},{"pid":"90ea16f94fd03a9c75804e016f0db9e12038c33c","tid":445320,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓，全球期待iPhone X</blockquote><br />\n期待 閱文招股多d</blockquote><br />\n老貓，點睇財經台有九成六人認為你係黑氣石？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442056/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442056/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1e5ef13343fc805990737223a1f0adfbcd23cb36","tid":445320,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:20:18.000Z","msg":"一早話佢只係一部5c <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72580cf6aeca6d0bd650c1e1ac29d73406969735","tid":445320,"uid":2795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"好彩一早買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba0908d75a6a95ce84b8ceca19235006aaf9f474","tid":445320,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:01:25.000Z","msg":"老貓睇埋呢單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\niPhone 8滯銷　內地零售商最多劈近800人仔 (19:42)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=mStNS%2BUU0P4YCm3kKkotsG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6b61a4f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內媒報道，iPhone 8/8 Plus在開售之初表現平平，不僅沒有出現了大排長龍、加價炒賣的情況，甚至在首發日就出現破發現象(零售價較官方價便宜200元人民幣)；而最新消息指，上述慘淡銷情僅僅是開端，目前iPhone 8國行版在內地第三方平台報價下跌達400至逾800元人民幣(下同)不等。<br />\n　　<br />\n在內地，某大電商最近舉行的iPhone 8活動也上，已經明確列出不同型號的iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus價格，均遠低於蘋果官方售價，減價最厲害的是iPhone 8 64GB金色版，原價5888元，目前只要4999元就可以帶回家，減價高達889元，像iPhone 8 Plus就全線一律減價400元。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說零售商網站顯示要立即搶購，但點擊進去就發現基本上都有貨，完全不需要搶購，可以說是大家連搶都懶得搶了。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘋果已經不再公布新品首發一周的銷量，而從第三方報告以及減價頻率來看，可以說iPhone 8/8 Plus銷售狀況之差遠超蘋果的想像。"},{"pid":"73f45f003ab62b39387ba2368d1868a13dbeed79","tid":445320,"uid":15730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"今次apple真係自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一早就唔出8出X就算啦 又要懶係有選擇咁 X又要懶係走貴價路線 點知普通路線既8質素參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb24375a3ff67752a3aa17a614ade47a6b1da68f","tid":445320,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老貓睇埋呢單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\niPhone 8滯銷　內地零售商最多劈近800人仔 (19:42)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=mStNS%2BUU0P4YCm3kKkotsG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6b61a4f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內媒報道，iPhone 8/8 Plus在開售之初表現平平，不僅沒有出現了大排長龍、加價炒賣的情況，甚至在首發日就出現破發現象(零售價較官方價便宜200元人民幣)；而最新消息指，上述慘淡銷情僅僅是開端，目前iPhone 8國行版在內地第三方平台報價下跌達400至逾800元人民幣(下同)不等。<br />\n　　<br />\n在內地，某大電商最近舉行的iPhone 8活動也上，已經明確列出不同型號的iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus價格，均遠低於蘋果官方售價，減價最厲害的是iPhone 8 64GB金色版，原價5888元，目前只要4999元就可以帶回家，減價高達889元，像iPhone 8 Plus就全線一律減價400元。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說零售商網站顯示要立即搶購，但點擊進去就發現基本上都有貨，完全不需要搶購，可以說是大家連搶都懶得搶了。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘋果已經不再公布新品首發一周的銷量，而從第三方報告以及減價頻率來看，可以說iPhone 8/8 Plus銷售狀況之差遠超蘋果的想像。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e46d150d625955c9477bf8ec199a64cc01bc2e1","tid":445320,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3496e29bb2035eaf4af7b77cdc2494d09ec247","tid":445320,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T13:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老貓睇埋呢單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\niPhone 8滯銷　內地零售商最多劈近800人仔 (19:42)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=mStNS%2BUU0P4YCm3kKkotsG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=6b61a4f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://on.cc</a>東網專訊】內媒報道，iPhone 8/8 Plus在開售之初表現平平，不僅沒有出現了大排長龍、加價炒賣的情況，甚至在首發日就出現破發現象(零售價較官方價便宜200元人民幣)；而最新消息指，上述慘淡銷情僅僅是開端，目前iPhone 8國行版在內地第三方平台報價下跌達400至逾800元人民幣(下同)不等。<br />\n　　<br />\n在內地，某大電商最近舉行的iPhone 8活動也上，已經明確列出不同型號的iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus價格，均遠低於蘋果官方售價，減價最厲害的是iPhone 8 64GB金色版，原價5888元，目前只要4999元就可以帶回家，減價高達889元，像iPhone 8 Plus就全線一律減價400元。<br />\n<br />\n雖然說零售商網站顯示要立即搶購，但點擊進去就發現基本上都有貨，完全不需要搶購，可以說是大家連搶都懶得搶了。<br />\n<br />\n另外，蘋果已經不再公布新品首發一周的銷量，而從第三方報告以及減價頻率來看，可以說iPhone 8/8 Plus銷售狀況之差遠超蘋果的想像。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />